# Third-party dependencies

LeVoice bundles or links the following open-source packages. Their licenses
are reproduced below where required.

| Package        | License    | Source                                              |
|----------------|------------|-----------------------------------------------------|
| WhisperKit     | MIT        | https://github.com/argmaxinc/WhisperKit             |
| FluidAudio     | Apache-2.0 | https://github.com/FluidInference/FluidAudio        |
| LLM.swift      | MIT        | https://github.com/obra/LLM.swift                   |
| Sparkle        | MIT        | https://github.com/sparkle-project/Sparkle          |

The Apache 2.0 license for FluidAudio requires distributing a NOTICE file
alongside binaries — fetch the upstream NOTICE before shipping a public DMG
and include it in the app bundle.
